name: Diversity
description:
"Diversity" presents the way humans tolerance and appreciate
the differences to be delivered through fashion.

This collection combine tenun ikat from Sikka Nusa Tenggara
Timur with natural fabrics such as lurik, linen and cotton. 

Every cut inspired by 90’s style. The colors will be khaki, navy blue, flame red and off white. The special features are sashiko embroidery, pin tucks and grossgrain.
